# Paperclip backup schedule (supercronic, container-native cron)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Timezone is controlled by the TZ env var set on the service in compose.
# Job output is redirected to PID 1's stdout/stderr so it shows up in
# `docker compose logs backup`.
#
# Field order: minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week  command
#
# Runs every day at 03:30 (container TZ).
30 3 * * * /usr/local/bin/backup.sh >> /proc/1/fd/1 2>> /proc/1/fd/2
